text: Kristin Cavallari (born January 5, 1987) is an American television and movie actress. She was in the television series Laguna Beach. She was also in the series The Hills. Cavallari was born in Denver, Colorado. She was raised in Barrington, Illinois. ==References== Category:Actors from Denver Category:Actors from Illinois Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:1987 births Category:Living people
